posts.caption: ALL the dim sum and then sum for #seilertospeiser 🥟🥟
Shrimp scampi swirl 🍝! What’s your favorite pasta? #EATINGNYC

Quite possibly the best fried rice I’ve ever had. Period. @nyumbai was rated one of America’s 10 best new restaurants in 2018 by @bonappetitmag and it certainly lived up to the hype and was worth the trek to Oakland. GO HERE!

#ad When you spend all year earning those @Chase Ultimate Rewards points, it’s fun to turn them into holiday gifts 🎁🎄 for friends and family. I can use Ultimate Rewards points to get gift cards for just about everyone on my list or to pay with points in the #ChasePay app. Either way, Chase is giving me #OneLessThing to stress about this holiday season!
#EATINGNYC
Because you are what you eat 🍝🍝🍝 HAPPY HALLOWEEN 🎃🖤// 📷: @joshkatz. #EATINGNYC
Lunch made easy thanks to ordering ahead through @chase pay 🍕🍕 - no lines and no waiting for when I’m on the go! #ChasePay #ChaseAmbassador #EATINGNYC

GUYS! Friendsgiving season is officially in full swing 🦃🙏 Very grateful for the epically delicious dinner I just had hosted by @bumblebff & @greatamericanturkeyco. Here’s to making the first move - in relationships, business and with friends in the year ahead 🥰💫 #EATINGNYC #bumblenyc #flipyourbird #beethankful
One of the world’s greatest debates: @shakeshack or @innout? Comment👇!
And after the Thanksgiving feast comes the sweet treats, I love indulging with some @baciperugina chocolates 🍫! Comment below with your favorite post-Thanksgiving dessert. #EATINGNYC
Do you ever just sit on your couch and think about pasta for like, a really long time? Asking for a friend.
Easy like Sunday morning 🥞🥞// Insanely good ricotta pancakes at the famous @plowsf.
Like for the ☀️ comment for the 🍣 and do both if you’re cold and hungry

Please proceed with caution ⚠️: The following video may result in feelings of extreme yearning, mood swings and excessive drooling. We recommend visiting @eatalyflatiron to cure these symptoms. #EATINGNYC
Nutella ricotta pizza for brunch kinda day 🍫🍕. Tag someone who’d love this! #EATINGNYC
A simply perfect strawberry + ricotta 🍓🍞 toast at the famed @tartinemanufactory. The chocolate chip cookie here was OOTW.

I have so much to be thankful for today and always 🙏🙏 : my loving family👩‍👧and friends 👯‍♀️👯‍♀️, my better half, best friend and huuusband @dpmatts 💑, and of course, all of you. It’s because of YOU that I get to wake up every single day and feel fulfilled doing what I love 📷🍽. Today, I’m also grateful to be an American 🇺🇸 (first gen) — to live a life with so much freedom is truly a blessing. ✌️, ❤️ & happy eating!
Love, Alexa
Kkwabaegi anyone? Just checked out @davidchang’s new spot @bangbar.xyz. Make sure to order one of these and a spicy pork bang 😎. See more on #InstagramStories. #EATINGNYC
BRUNCH: This month’s @blackseedbagels X @viacarota 🥯 which is straight🔥 - speck, stracchino cheese, butternut squash and cabbage salad. #EATINGNYC
A taste of Bollywood in SoHo - incredibly good fast-casual Indian spot just opened. Must orders include this totally tikka Frankie and chickpea fritters. #EATINGNYC

MARK YOUR CALENDARS: I’m hosting a bake sale next Friday, 11/30, @smiletogonyc at the Freehand Hotel for @nokidhungry starting at 8AM! We have an EPIC line up including sweets from @breadsbakery, @dominiqueansel, @chipnewyorkcity, @dailyprov, @westbourne, @caffemarchio and @quality_eats! Can’t wait to see you all there and to support this amazing cause 🍪🧁🍩🍰!!!

Gluten-free tahini brownies made with @mightysesameco ! I love tahini because it’s so versatile and the perfect addition to sweets like these super fudgey brownies made with healthy alternatives like coconut oil and agave nectar. Link in bio for recipe 👩‍🍳🍫 #EATINGNYC
Feels like yesterday! Happy 6 months @dpmatts - thank you for making life, LIFE, for being the greatest friend and husband and for starting all our mornings with an epic dance party ❤️
TOMORROW!! Come to @smiletogonyc @freehandhotels for an epic bake sale benefitting @nokidhungry! Can’t wait to meet some of you there starting at 8AM 🍪🧁🍩🍰!

#chaseambassador That moment when you realize you just killed it at life: leaving my apt without my wallet 🤭 & using #chasepay to find somewhere to eat near me and then paying for lunch on the app too. There was even an offer that got automatically applied – life made easy!! Thanks @chase. #EATINGNYC

Because I can't get enough Chicken Joy 🍗 & Jolly Spaghetti 🍝: I'm GIVING AWAY a $120 @jollibeeus gift card for you to use at their first Manhattan location! Like this photo and tag a friend below for a chance to win. GIVEAWAY CLOSED! Winner: @jamworth. #EATINGNYC #ad
Oh man. Sunday scaries are furrrrreal this week 🙈🐶
Oodles of spicy lamb noodles at NYC’s best quick-casual Xi’an spot @xianfoods. #EATINGNYC

#ad WOAH. If you close your eyes and believe when biting into these flavor packed lime and cracked pepper chips, I'm pretty sure you'll end up on a beach in Mexico. Thanks for adding some thrill to my Sunday @RedRockDeli. Photo: @lily_nyc2555 #EATINGNYC #RedRockDeli #SnackingFantastic
NEW POST: NYC’s best sweet shops 🍭🍬🍭 link in bio! 📷: @lily_nyc255. #EATINGNYC
Alla vodka 🍕, all day everyday! Tee coming in 2019 😍// 📷: @joshkatz. #EATINGNYC
Tomorrow NYC’s first Nutella cafe will open. Obviously everything + Nutella tastes good but their homemade Nutella whipped cream (served on hot chocolate, etc) was phenomenal! #EATINGNYC
Classic triple scoop, SF style: secret breakfast, chocolate malt and peanut butter ripple 😎
✨Monday night lights✨

#ad anyone else wish they were doing this right now? 🙋🏻‍♀️🙋🏻‍♀️ Pro Tip: step up your beach situation with @redrockdeli’s red curry coconut chips and pair them with a fresh coconut water 🥥🌴 - epic combo 😎! #RedRockDeli #SnackingFantastic
If you can’t tell, we’re very happy and full after making (and eating) our own custom 🍰! Can’t think of a better way to spend a snowy Thursday ❄️⛄️. Happy birthday @milkbarstore 🎉❤️!! #EATINGNYC

Would you believe me if I told you this 🍕 tastes even better than it looks? @mamas_too is definitely worth the hype - they combine all the things I love about pizza: a doughy center, crispy edges, a somewhat sweet sauce and super cheesy throughout. I tried almost every slice here and am having a hard time picking favorites...but this spicy pepperoni is definitely up there. Picking a photo to post from here was exceptionally challenging because too, come on, this is so beautiful 😍. You did good @mamas_too. #EATINGNYC

Here’s me fishing for dinner tonight @zauo_ny 🎣! You get to choose what kind of fish you’d like to catch, fish for it and then choose how you want it prepared. Such a fun experience and definitely great for groups. We need more fun restaurants like this! #EATINGNYC

The double cheeseburger (and the stunning chandeliers✨) was def the star of the show here, which is no surprise bc @brendansodikoff of @auchevalchicago is behind this spot 🍔🍟. Also served with that insanely good garlic aioli...#IYKYK. #EATINGNYC
Finally checked out @shakeshack’s new innovation kitchen where they’re doing really cool things like hot chicken sandwiches and chicken nugs 👌👌 #EATINGNYC
That good good hot 🔥🍯🍕#EATINGNYC
